<br>
Once you got your charcter to 50 I think you became an Avatar and got the chance to remort. When you remorted you lost all your skills from pervious the class  and became a lvl 1 agian of the class you picked. After completing all the classes (6 if i remember right) You got all the powers of the classes.<br>
<br>
This was a good idea for a texted based mud but I don't see it as a good idea in EQ. <p><center><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=104908 target="_blank"><img src=http://www.circleofpride.com/files/vandrimsig.gif></center></a>

